window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Having been offered the dubious salvation of a sect that worships his late mother, Nemesis finds himself in a position of having to decide who to trust, and who to kill. With his partners at his side, the black dragon will continue to advance his cultivation and grow in power.</p> <p>No matter who stands in his way.</p> <p>The Order of Nightshade might think they know how to guide him, but Nemesis is going to show them that underestimating a dragon is a mistake you only make once.</p>"; 
